I am trying to keep it in the area of the optional shelf, it is 7" tall and 
doesn't come out past the front of the dash, I am over 6' tall but have 
really short legs (can't find shirts that fit) and I have been driving it 
around with the cardboard speaker for 2 days and have yet to have made 
contact, and somehow it hasn't fallen off the dash, which is pretty weird, I 
am trying to live with it for a week before continuing.

> There are quite a few places where you can hang the box.  I hung my shelf
> from the lip of the dash and from existing screws on the air duct.
