I am going to put in blind 3/8-16 inserts and try to figure out mounts at 
each end and in the middle, the middle looks easy, I plan to come off the 
frame piece that is on each side of the E-brake.

It will probably weigh around 25 pounds before we pile junk in the cubby 
holes.

The design will require a groove in the back for the E-brake to fit in, I 
think this will add a lot of strength.

